{"tid":2119282,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"阿媽誤會咗我表哥入HKU","createTime":"2020-07-22T04:20:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-23T16:12:04.000Z","uid":154406,"like":907,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":86,"replies":[{"pid":"002fba68b8d76eca6bf331d35645ca5a4a51c65c","tid":2119282,"uid":154406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T04:20:45.000Z","msg":"是咁的 <br />\n<br />\n我表哥佢今年考dse，琴日放榜 <br />\n佢考得唔係太好，又怕呀媽擔心 <br />\n呀媽一生人既夢想佢佢個仔入大學 <br />\n因為佢d親戚街坊都無仔女入到U <br />\n<br />\n今日一早番左屋企時，呀媽係咁問佢成績點，夠唔夠分, 可以入邊間U <br />\n表哥心情唔好，是撚但但同呀媽佢佢去讀藥劑， <br />\n之後請入房訓較(尋晚通左頂) <br />\n<br />\n表哥起左身，屙完屎之後出黎 <br />\n發現成家人都好開心，呀爸呀媽叫撚晒佢d親戚姑嫂話今晚出黎食飯 <br />\n同個仔慶祝入到HKU讀藥劑 <br />\n<br />\n依個時候先知大撚獲 <br />\n表哥其實係去報IVE讀藥劑 <br />\n唔撚知邊個親戚街坊話係香港既大學，只有HKU有藥劑讀 <br />\n所以呀媽以為佢夠分入左HKU <br />\n<br />\n屌你 <br />\n我表哥頭先打電話比我 <br />\n問我點做好......... <br />\n<br />\n點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25aa2ea10713df6b840c8f1195d043ddbcc7b7da","tid":2119282,"uid":255525,"like":879,"dislike":10,"score":869,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T04:24:00.000Z","msg":"我諗你表哥都畢左業幾年..仔都生埋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cd5c77cbe3f11806be84cdf3bc921892a153f36","tid":2119282,"uid":306018,"like":25,"dislike":190,"score":-165,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T04:25:25.000Z","msg":"潮文來的"},{"pid":"14d5af3005113e86670f062cf35ac2340eefbce9","tid":2119282,"uid":209773,"like":367,"dislike":4,"score":363,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T04:33:57.000Z","msg":"你表哥個仔都藥劑畢業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"399a0a4d0d4df409d7330bb9d2b798b478dc02d7","tid":2119282,"uid":29836,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T0