,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T08:56:59.000Z","msg":"一年真係過得快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56701e42d8edb0e117efedc83b385e1e04cb2b23","tid":2119282,"uid":200135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T08:57:45.000Z","msg":"年經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c539d432c21d02ac3bd157d775fb703ddf5b7d1b","tid":2119282,"uid":58645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"002fba68b8d76eca6bf331d35645ca5a4a51c65c","tid":2119282,"uid":154406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T04:20:45.000Z","msg":"是咁的 <br />\n<br />\n我表哥佢今年考dse，琴日放榜 <br />\n佢考得唔係太好，又怕呀媽擔心 <br />\n呀媽一生人既夢想佢佢個仔入大學 <br />\n因為佢d親戚街坊都無仔女入到U <br />\n<br />\n今日一早番左屋企時，呀媽係咁問佢成績點，夠唔夠分, 可以入邊間U <br />\n表哥心情唔好，是撚但但同呀媽佢佢去讀藥劑， <br />\n之後請入房訓較(尋晚通左頂) <br />\n<br />\n表哥起左身，屙完屎之後出黎 <br />\n發現成家人都好開心，呀爸呀媽叫撚晒佢d親戚姑嫂話今晚出黎食飯 <br />\n同個仔慶祝入到HKU讀藥劑 <br />\n<br />\n依個時候先知大撚獲 <br />\n表哥其實係去報IVE讀藥劑 <br />\n唔撚知邊個親戚街坊話係香港既大學，只有HKU有藥劑讀 <br />\n所以呀媽以為佢夠分入左HKU <br />\n<br />\n屌你 <br />\n我表哥頭先打電話比我 <br />\n問我點做好......... <br />\n<br />\n點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T08:58:41.000Z","msg":"而家點出街食飯"},{"pid":"e19c33b8b0ac428d050a86b8cd4cc700ddf6884c","tid":2119282,"uid":34209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T09:26:45.000Z","msg":"年年呢個時間都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cebed83ad4dda0b148461b2bba2874ec3b364daa","tid":2119282,"uid":116917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T10:01:14.000Z","msg":"年經"},{"pid":"957d7e263ceb06aa555c15e029ba9f91dd0d5936","tid":2119282,"uid":284264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T10:23:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\"